706911f-a.title: Brooklyn: Stockholm Street - Bushwick Avenue
706911f-a.text:
A rear view of buildings on Stockholk Street, south side, between Bush-
wick and Evergreen Aves. (Andrew Stockholw sold these sites to William
Coil in 1855).
1897.
Eugene L Armbruster Collectien.
MAY BE REPRODUCED.
